snippet: Kenny Miller scored in the 83rd minute to give the Vancouver Whitecaps their second win in nearly three months, a 2-1 victory over the Red Bulls in Harrison, N.J.
abstract: Vancouver Whitecaps earn a 2-1 victory over the New Jersey Red Bulls; other soccer news noted.
